io.github.andreaszks.ergasales.model

Class Sale

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.andreaszks.ergasales.model.Sale
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Sale
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a Sale. Sales are managed through SaleRegistry

    A sale is created only through SaleRegistry.createSale(LocalDate, String, List, String, float)
    and is only updated through SaleRegistry.updateSale(String, LocalDate, float, String, List)
